```
def main_function():
     previous_job = None
     while not stop_event.is_set():
         current_job = process_job(..., previous=previous_job)
         # ...
         previous_job = current_job

@retry(stop=stop_after_attempt(3))
def process_job(..., previous=None):
    ...
```

